    "Irregular wide-complex tachycardia at very high rate (>200 bpm)",
    "Grossly irregular RR intervals (irregular irregularity)",
    "Wide bizarre QRS complexes (delta wave + accessory pathway conduction)",
    "Rate can exceed 300 bpm - ventricular fibrillation risk",
    "ECG looks chaotic - often misidentified as VF or VT"
  ],
  "measurements": {
    "rate": "200–300 bpm (dangerously fast)",
    "rhythm": "Irregular (irregular irregularity)",
